{"tid":1536021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"帶人圍狗屋係臥底行動一環","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:23:09.000Z","uid":4672,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b31fe2c8531884fc1815ffcf0f5c77a1ec8716cd","tid":1536021,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:21:48.000Z","msg":"成堆警犬臥底帶節奏 搞到街坊又跟 示威者又跟 勇武手足又要跟<br />\n玩咗咁多日圍狗屋 點解仲係唔明? <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n班狗最中意你地企曬一個點 等佢地完成佈處 然後東街出防暴 西街收網</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">說好的BE WATER呢?</span></span><br />\n一次就可以拉十幾件 而且對社會冇破壞力 不影響政府 <br />\n圍狗屋冇意思 不如塞馬路 快閃主要幹道 更容易比到壓力政府"},{"pid":"3d56911dd90951e43a032db8c4f75d23360ab667","tid":1536021,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06fa8d64773ee93e68cac4293487872a9ebe9222","tid":1536021,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:22:40.000Z","msg":"大家認真睇下邊個帶人去送頭  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caef0e0c471e06c5e0b38032556d8375884cb10b","tid":1536021,"uid":47222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:23:46.000Z","msg":"係 部分光復行動都係 <br />\n<br />\n機場907戰術：全部唔中途落車唔黑衫拖gip/接機 有車出車<br />\n到左就入返東涌再流水式入機場 或者機鐵唔落車<br />\n如果有必要情況下要set roadblock既set完即走做返市民<br />\n冇車走就商場shopping食飯唔洗心虛 等家長接<br />\n琴日證實青馬塞車會塞班警犬增援 不必過份擔心<br />\n<br />\n908 美領"},{"pid":"568a203b243ef827264522c52d7ae616467374f9","tid":1536021,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:23:49.000Z","msg":"各位手足醒下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da2c55db5049f409c0686df01f52cefdba86094","tid":1536021,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"再中計就真係會比人拉曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c6a36a2d4c29e76ca0f7468a3652cfa5ec2eae","tid":1536021,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:26:07.000Z","msg":"推啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e82c03ae3ed2603a85b5fd6520f1993d4d90c69","tid":1536021,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"請君入urn  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\